STELLAR ALIGNMENT:
Veyru treatments are affected by the position of reference star SAGWE392. The correct treatment procedure and its specific parameters (hold duration, which face to start on, pressure level) change every round based on the stellar alignment. Only the engineer has the stellar reader and knows the correct treatment and parameters for each round. Even if symptoms look familiar from a previous round, the correct treatment and parameters may be completely different. You must always get instructions from the engineer — never assume you know the correct procedure.
